---

<section
  class="bg-light-lily section w-full overflow-hidden px-5 py-16 lg:py-20"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <header>
      <SectionTitle style="dark" mobile="true" class="anim-title">
        Cobertura de evento
